Package uk.ac.aber.dcs.sta17.cs12420.as.model

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GameModelInterface
    This interface describes the behaviour of a hangman type of game To be used in CS124 individual assignment
    WordListInterface
    This class here was designed with the idea in mind that for both for example a GUI version and a text based version could use the same list, rather than having to close and open there own individual ones.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GameModel
    This is the basic GameModel interface which is to serve as the game basic core.
    WordList
    Contains List of all the words to pick from.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    EmptyListException
    This exception is created with the intension of appearing if game play is attempted when the list is 0, thus contains 0 words or phrases.
    GameOverException
    This exception is created with the intension of appearing if game play is attempted when it is actually over or similar circumstances.
